# PCB Manufacturing Tracker

A full-stack Manufacturing Execution System (MES) for tracking PCB boards through multiple manufacturing stages.

## 🚀 Features

- **Kanban Board** - Visual tracking of all boards
- **Process Steps** - Soldering → Optical Inspection → X-Ray → Testing → Repair
- **User Roles** - Admin, Manager, Supervisor, Operator
- **Image Upload** - Attach photos to each manufacturing step
- **Dashboard** - Real-time statistics and charts
- **Notifications** - Get notified when boards are assigned
- **CSV Export** - Export all data to Excel-compatible format

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Python, FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, SQLite
- **Frontend:** React, Material UI, Vite

## 🔐 Default Users

| Username | Password | Role |
|----------|----------|------|
| admin | admin123 | Administrator |
| manager1 | manager123 | Manager |
| operator1 | operator123 | Operator |

